Dialogue: 0,00:19:55.07,00:19:55.46,ayano ch,,0,0,0,,{\pos(744,682)}我说
Dialogue: 0,00:19:57.28,00:19:57.75,ayano ch,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,00:19:58.97,00:20:00.13,shintaro ch,,0,0,0,,不 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,00:20:01.91,00:20:03.50,shintaro ch,,0,0,0,,没什么 忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,00:20:05.15,00:20:05.85,ayano ch,,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,00:20:06.32,00:20:07.40,shintaro ch,,0,0,0,,都说了没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,00:20:08.00,00:20:09.09,shintaro ch,,0,0,0,,话说 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,00:20:09.67,00:20:11.02,shintaro ch,,0,0,0,,反正大家早晚都会跟过来的
Dialogue: 0,00:20:12.30,00:20:13.97,ayano ch,,0,0,0,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,00:20:14.27,00:20:19.12,ayano ch,,0,0,0,,真是的 总是这么自我 这样可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,00:20:19.44,00:20:20.25,shintaro ch,,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,00:20:24.71,00:20:25.35,ayano ch,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,00:20:27.02,00:20:28.48,shintaro ch,,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,00:20:28.78,00:20:31.42,ene ch,,0,0,0,,喂 你们别在那打情骂俏了
Dialogue: 0,00:20:31.72,00:20:35.94,kano ch,,0,0,0,,是啊 都已经这么热了 饶了我们吧
Dialogue: 0,00:20:36.82,00:20:39.67,ayano ch,,0,0,0,,不 不是你们想的那样啦
Dialogue: 0,00:20:42.15,00:20:43.50,ayano ch,,0,0,0,,伸太郎 走吧
Dialogue: 0,00:20:47.53,00:20:47.79,shintaro ch,,0,0,0,,好的
